  "title": "Structure Engineer #79350",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Construction</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Structure Engineer</strong></li><li>Working Location: Expo</li><li>Working Hours: 5 days (Mon – Fri, 9.00am – 6.45pm)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic salary up to $6,500 + AWS + Variable Bonus</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent Role</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Prepare design calculations for building façades using design software.</li><li>Perform structural calculations and simulations to ensure compliance with relevant building codes and specifications.</li><li>Work with the design team and quantity surveyors to resolve structural issues for façade works.</li><li>Review architectural drawings and develop practical façade design solutions that meet the design intent and are buildable.</li><li>Collaborate with consultants, the Professional Engineer (PE), and the Accredited Checker (AC) on structural matters, ensuring alignment with shop drawings for submission.</li><li>Prepare and manage BCA submissions for approval.</li><li>Maintain records in line with ISO/OHSAS procedures.</li><li>Carry out other duties as assigned by management.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Bachelor’s or Master’s degree in Civil/Structural Engineering, Mechanical Engineering, or a related field.</li><li>Proficient with structural analysis software.</li><li>Able to read and interpret technical drawings and architectural plans.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#79350 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Rachael Lee | EA Reg No.: R2093131</p>",
